OL,3,CJubilation for Cardiff City after
OL,4,Csecuring promotion back to the
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,FCardiff clinched automatic promotion
OL,8,Fback to the Championship with a 3-1
OL,9,FLeague One victory at Reading.
OL,11,FExeter goalkeeper Jack Bycroft's
OL,12,Fstoppage-time leveller against
OL,13,FStockport meant all of Cardiff's
OL,14,Fpromotion rivals failed to win,
OL,15,Fenabling the Welsh side to clinch a
OL,16,Freturn to the second tier.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
