OL,3,CJubilation for Cardiff City after
OL,4,Csecuring promotion back to the
OL,5,CChampionship
OL,7,FBut Ng's superb angled effort from 20
OL,8,Fyards settled the issue as Cardiff's
OL,9,F2,935 fans celebrated wildly.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
